snippet.title: Phantom Rose Scarlet Teaser
snippet.description:
A free roguelike card adventure. Play as Reina, a maid in a mansion ravaged by evil creatures. Build your card deck and make careful decisions while you explore as each death may be permanent.

◆ Free on Apple AppStore: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1502851569
◆ Free on Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.phantomrosegame.phantomRoseScarlett

◆ Twitter: https://twitter.com/phantomrosegame
◆ Website: https://phantomrosegame.com
